                Are you fed up with unreliable contractors who do a substandard job? Are you worried that your office or commercial building is looking old? Do you need to add more colour to your business space? Look no further. Our commercial painting services are available for clients in the GTA. At Bottega Construction, we believe that a fresh coat of paint can bring new life to your commercial space. Commercial buildings are typically large and require a big staff and time on the part of painters. Our company offers predictability and peace of mind that will not have you bogged down with the minute details of a painting job.





